            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052562/Dijk en Zoete, Fotografische Termen en Technieken (1984)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052566/Hogenboom, handleiding voor het registreren en uitwisselen (1994</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>一種沖印相片的技法過程，以混合重鉻酸鹽和阿拉伯膠製成的膠質乳劑做為感光劑，以色料做為最後成像的材料，感光之後乳劑硬化形成影像，再將未硬化的乳劑以水沖顯影，露出形成在紙基上的高亮部分和中間色調。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Procedimento di stampa fotografica al pigmento, nel quale la sostanza è gomma arabica sensibilizzata con bicromato di potassio divenendo insolubile in acqua dopo l'esposizione al sole.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Italian</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
